  If any portion of section 7 is held invalid or unenforceable under
certain circumstances, that invalidation or unenforceability shall not
invalidate the rest of section 7 or the remainder of this License;
instead, such circumstances shall be interpreted in the manner which
most closely approximates an absolute world-wide royalty-free patent
